#PLY Primitive creator/mesh constructor

If using the mesh constructor, put your PLY files into the "input" folder.

This program needs conda to run. 
use the commands in the following order

##First time setup
wget https://repo.anaconda.com/archive/Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh
bash Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh
export PATH=~/anaconda3/bin:$PATH
conda install -c conda-forge point_cloud_utils

##Running the program after installation
export PATH=~/anaconda3/bin:$PATH
conda activate base
python
>> import point_cloud_utils
>> exit()
conda deactivate

conda activate base
python plymain.py